::Kluster::

Kluster nods, sending Phobia the coordinates of a hatch, which begins to open 
with the press of a button. All exits to that hatch save one are locked, 
Kluster walking off down a corridor. He switches his comm to transmit to 
Hysteria.

"Hysteria, please meet me in landing bay 1," he says into his comm-link, then 
switching it back to Phobia's frequency, "Me and another bot will be waiting 
for you."
